{"product_id":"berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Light Natural Glow Cream 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover Berrichi face cream Light – natural radiance and balance for your skin. Face cream Light is a light and silky cream designed to moisturise and protect combination and normal skin on a daily basis. It helps to restore the skin’s natural moisture balance, evens the texture and supports the skin’s natural defences, leaving skin radiant and soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Light Natural Glow Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLight and fast-absorbing texture that does not clog pores\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep moisturising action that restores the skin’s moisture balance\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes irritations and soothes inflamed skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmoothes the skin tone, reducing wrinkles and pigmentation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAnti-ageing\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cu\u003eFurcellaran\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/u\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRough Razor Beard\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– with antibacterial properties, it helps soothe and protect the skin, promoting a smoother, brighter complexion.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor combined and normal skin\u003c\/span\u003e. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. Suitable as a foundation for make-up, it can also be used at night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin**, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Helianthus Annuus Seed oil\/Polyglyceryl-3 Palmitate\/Usnea Barbata extract (Usnea Barbata), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe glass bottle and pump system are reusable.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51042379202887,"sku":null,"price":30.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-30ml-286537.png?v=1739897155","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-30ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}